edu.uoc.som.jarvis.plugins.discord

Class JarvisDiscordUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uoc.som.jarvis.plugins.discord.JarvisDiscordUtils

  • public class JarvisDiscordUtils
extends Object
    An utility class that holds Discord-related helpers.

    This class defines the jarvis configuration key to store the Discord bot token, as well as an utility method to retrieve an existing instance of the JDA client, in order to avoid multiple client instantiations.

    • Method Detail

      • getJDA

        public static net.dv8tion.jda.core.JDA getJDA(String token)
        Returns the JDA client associated to the provided token.

        This method returns the stored jda client if its token corresponds to the provided one. If not, this method creates a new JDA instance and overrides the existing one.

        Parameters:
        token - the Discord bot token to retrieve the JDA client for
        Returns:
        the JDA client associated to the provided token
